<body>

<div id="topic_content">
		
<p></p>
<p class="rvps2"><span class="rvts11">Company Settings</span></p>
<p class="rvps2"><span class="rvts11"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps2"><span class="rvts11"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class="rvts11"> - </span><span class="rvts42">This module allows the authorized users to setup company details. This includes the following:</span></p>
<p class="rvps2"><span class="rvts6"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps2"><span class="rvts23"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps3"><img width="806" height="390" alt="" style="padding : 1px; background-color : #000000;" src="lib/NewItem8.png"></p>
<p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts13"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts13"><br/></span></p>
<ol style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: decimal;">
<li value="1" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Company Name - required; user input</span></li>
<li value="2" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Acronym - required; user input</span></li>
<li value="3" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Tag Line - user input</span></li>
<li value="4" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Contact Number - user input</span></li>
<li value="5" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Email Address - user input</span></li>
<li value="6" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Address</span></li>
</ol>
<ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;"><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: circle;">
<li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps53"><span class="rvts13">Street - user input</span></li>
<li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps53"><span class="rvts13">City/Municipality - required; with fixed value; filtered by province; based on the list of city/municipalities in the Philippines.</span></li>
<li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps53"><span class="rvts13">Barangay - required; with fixed value; filtered by city/municipality; based on the list of barangays in the Philippines.</span></li>
<li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps53"><span class="rvts13">Province - required; with fixed value; filtered by region; based on the list of provinces in the Philippines.</span></li>
<li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps53"><span class="rvts13">Region - required; with fixed value; based on the list of regions in the Philippines.</span></li>
</ul></ul>
<ol style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: decimal;">
<li value="7" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Company Logo - this will allow user to upload the company logo.</span></li>
<li value="8" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Contact Person - required; user input</span></li>
<li value="9" style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps50"><span class="rvts13">Remarks - user input</span></li>
</ol>
<p class="rvps5"><span class="rvts13"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps6"><span class="rvts13"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts23"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps2"><span class="rvts23"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps5"><img width="70" height="91" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="lib/help2.jpg"><span class="rvts11">How to use Company Settings?</span></p>
<p class="rvps21"><span class="rvts13">1.</span><span class="rvts11"> &nbsp;</span><span class="rvts13">Provide company's details like company name, Acronym,Tag Line, Contact Number, Email Addess. Street, City,Municipality, Barangay, Province,</span></p>
<p class="rvps21"><span class="rvts13">Region, Contact Person, and Remarks. Provide all the necessary details needed of the system please be careful with the fields, all fields marked </span></p>
<p class="rvps21"><span class="rvts13">with (</span><span class="rvts28">*</span><span class="rvts13">) is required so you better put data on it so that you can proceed on saving.</span></p>
<p class="rvps21"><span class="rvts13">2. Click Save button located on the upper left of the form.</span></p>
<p class="rvps5"><span class="rvts11"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps2"><img width="70" height="91" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="lib/help2.jpg"><span class="rvts11"> How to upload company logo?</span></p>
<p class="rvps13"><span class="rvts13">1. &nbsp;Click "folder" icon </span><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="lib/NewItem7.png"><span class="rvts13"> &nbsp;to open a folder where your company logo is located</span></p>
<p class="rvps13"><span class="rvts13"><br/></span></p>
<p class="rvps13"><span class="rvts13">2. &nbsp;Click "save" button to save settings</span></p>
<p></p>
</div>
	
	</body>
	
</html>

